Program: Discovery
Title: Circadian rhythms
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrxpy
Last Broadcast Date: 03 October 2000
The importance of the human body's natural clock or circadian rhythms. We all live our lives at the centre of a triangle of time, including a clock, a schedule and our own biological clock. The programme looks at what we can do to make sure our body rhythm keeps step with our lives.